{"tid":1506862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日發夢就嚟頂唔順","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:11:14.000Z","uid":240705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a6556fd534d001fb51183f5cf9846d5daa66161d","tid":1506862,"uid":240705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"份工就嚟頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為成日請假發夢 <br />\n淨係呢個月都已經請左四次病假一次事假<br />\n每次仲要比幾百蚊睇私家醫生<br />\n當然我老細都應該就嚟頂唔順我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點係因為六日都要返工 <br />\n冇得出所以先去請假<br />\n但由於屋企原因冇錢又唔得<br />\n因為屋企人傷殘要大量家用養住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本人住九龍區<br />\n跪求60up起甚至70以上兼職介紹<br />\n平日可以日做十小時或以上個種<br />\n好多高薪兼職都冇咁長時間可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616be0cc99542f8ded049cbed3ed6816039e55d1","tid":1506862,"uid":240705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea7795e34311131fa2d94834146441f91940c96","tid":1506862,"uid":240705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:45:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679a1d73aaf175b4fb28d434ba1809125fdc8f1e","tid":1506862,"uid":269991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:47:15.000Z","msg":"P牌幫唔到你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce227595b3bb7da2cd4abd2aaf45858417af35c0","tid":1506862,"uid":250164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}